import React from 'react'
import { Container } from './Cart.element'

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <NavContainer>
            <NavLogo></NavLogo>
            <NavCheckOutSteps></NavCheckOutSteps>
            <NavSecure></NavSecure>
        </NavContainer>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Cart
